msgstr "在开发模式下运行 ` `mvn clean quarkus:dev` ` 后，若在浏览器中访问 link:http://localhost:8080/health/ready[http://localhost:8080/health/ready，] 您应该会看到类似以下内容的输出："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
